On the Moon, the Vok Transformer senses that the remains of the 
energon sphere are being manipulated.

Meteara: This does not bode well. Should the Cybertronians find out 
the true purpose of the spheres, they may try to destroy them, or 
worse... I will have to intervene.

She turns towards the the rimward part of the galaxy and transmits her 
plan of action to her Vok masters. After doing this, she ignites her 
thrusters and takes off for the position of Kup and Sunhawk.
